text: manusyanige sankatavenadaru eduradaga avanu malagidallu, kulitallu, nintallu nam'mannu kareyalarambhisuttane. Adare navu avana a sankatavannu nivarisidaga avanu, tanna sankatada vele tanendu nam'mannu karede iralillavo embante nadedu biduttane. I riti atirekavesaguvavarige, avaru maduvudellavannu navu candaganisibidutteve
